We use this information:
- to enable the retrieval and visit of the website;
- to continuously improve our website and offerings and to further adapt them to the
  needs of our users;
- to carry out internal quality controls;
- to detect, eliminate and prevent errors, malfunctions and possible misuse;
- to generate statistics on access channels and site usage. In so far the collection of the data is not technically necessary, the legal basis for
the collection of the data is based on consent pursuant to Article 6 (1) lit. a GDPR.

